import NewAnecdote from './components/AnecdoteForm' import AnecdoteList from './components/AnecdoteList' import Notification from './components/Notification' import Filter from './components/Filter' import anecdoteService from './services/anecdotes' import { useDispatch } from 'react-redux' import { useEffect } from 'react' import { setAnecdotes } from './reducers/anecdoteReducer' const App = () => { const dispatch = useDispatch() useEffect(() => { anecdoteService .getAll().then(anecdotes => dispatch(setAnecdotes(anecdotes))) }, []) return (

Anecdotes

) } export default App
